cast.name: 丹尼尔·阿劳兹 Daniel Aráoz

introduction: Teenager Nati lives in a humble neighborhood along with her brother Sebas. They distribute the food that their mother Mary makes, but this work fails to pay off her family's debt. Therefore, the two siblings decide to join a gang led by Yuca, an old man who carries out various crimes in the neighborhood, in a way too aggressive. The rebellion of Nati will cause conflicts in the group and the boss will turn his anger on her. But she will not stay with her arms crossed and will not forgive them.
